usiasm (10%)\\r\\n\\r\\nBegin the interview now with your introduction.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Hi! I\'m Sarah, and I\'ll be conducting your technical interview today. To start, could you briefly introduce yourself and tell me what excites you most about the MERN Stack Intern role?\"}]', 1, 3, 'active', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-01-27 04:19:46', NULL, NULL),
